You are hereHomeInvest With UsCorporate Services 


Corporate Services 

Retirement Plan Review for Sponsors
We will conduct a review of a plans structure, investments and fees to ensure it meets an appropriate fiduciary standard now required by corporate plans.
Corporate Plan Consultation
We will work with the plan sponsor to choose the appropriate plan (i.e. 401(k), 403(b), 457, SEP, SIMPLE) and help structure the plan’s design to optimize employee deferral and satisfaction.
Co-Fiduciary Advisory Service
As a 3(21) Fiduciary, we will conduct employee education, initiate quarterly plan reviews for management and keep abreast of the regulatory changes in the industry.











